content.rendered:
Directed by Pawan Wadeyar

Written by Pawan Wadeyar

Cast Puneeth Rajkumar (Gagan Dixit). Saroja Devi B.(Self). Anupama Parameswaran (Shruti (as Anupama Parameshwaran)). Rachita Ram (Sakshi). Chikkanna (Keshav). Pradeep Doddaiah (News anchor). Sadhu Kokila (Namadev). Srinivasa Murthy. P. Ravi Shankar (Ghanashyam Yadav). Urvashi H.V.(Journalist (uncredited))

Languages Kannada

Production Rockline Entertainment
